description:
Beverly finds a box whilst digging in her garden on Christmas Eve. Inside the box is the corpse of a small strange creature. It is not long before Beverly is feeling very ill, and a sinister presence has inhabited her home for Christmas.

Contains strong language and scenes of horror. XVID compressed.

